==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Water lemon
<hw>Wa"ter lem"on</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The edible
fruit of two species of passion flower (<spn>Passiflora
laurifolia</spn>, and <spn>Passiflora maliformis</spn>); -- so called in
the West Indies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Waterless</ent>⟦br⟧
